# demos/vision.tape — Image attachment for multimodal models
Output demos/vision.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "hello"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "/image screenshot.png"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "what's in this screenshot? any UI issues?"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "exit"
Enter
